| PyPI | https://pypi.org/project/misata/ |

**Key APIs covered in this notebook:**

- `misata.generate(story)` → `dict[str, DataFrame]`
- `misata.parse(story)` → `SchemaConfig`
- `misata.generate_from_schema(schema)` → `dict[str, DataFrame]`
- `misata.generate_timeseries(story)` → `DataFrame`
- `misata.validate_csv(path)` → `CsvValidationReport`
- `misata.detect_locale(story)` → locale code
- `misata.get_locale_pack(locale)` → `LocalePack`
- `misata.load_yaml_schema(path)` → `SchemaConfig`</cell id="next-header">
